snippet.title: Moroi Springs | Winterlore Chapter I - Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a glimpse of Winterlore, the first game in the Moroi Springs universe. Out now on iOS, Android, PC & Mac! Links below 🔽

Help young Ozana on her journey of self-discovery in this short adventure game. Embark on a quest to fill a dowry trunk and discover the lost folklore behind Winterlore.

----------

Download the game:
⇸ iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/winterlore-i/id1500119397?mt=8
⇸ PC & Mac: https://moroisprings.itch.io/zestre
⇸ Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.moroisprings.winterlore

Stay in touch
⇸ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MoroiSprings/
⇸ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/moroisprings/
⇸ Web: https://www.moroisprings.com/

🖤MS
